   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>I make it manifest to you (that I have sold) first the house with site to Aurelius from Oxyrhynchus ... on the twentieth of the month Payni, at the price of 1600 drachmas with ... Theon paid as an agreement (or: reconciliation) ... on the same twentieth or on a day ... Later (he paid ... ) ......... instead of 560 drachmas from me ...</ab>
